 use of ceritinib with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors should generally be avoided.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/61060/', '', 'Tinidazole, Tetracycline, Sucralfate, Misoprostol, Bismuth subcitrate potassium, Amoxicillin, Lincomycin, Dirithromycin', 'Alpelisib, Trametinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Alectinib', 1767369485);
