CYP450 3A4 inhibitors should generally be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/61072/', '', 'Pegloticase, Febuxostat, Rasburicase, Probenecid, Allopurinol', 'Dabrafenib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pexidartinib, Avapritinib, Bosutinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, Cobimetinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, More', 1767369485);
